# Offer of Internship — AI Intern

Omninuera  
[Date]

Dear [Candidate Name],

We are pleased to offer you the position of **AI Intern** at Omninuera on the following terms.

## Position and Duration
- **Role:** AI Intern (fixed-term internship)  
- **Duration:** 3 months  
- **Start Date:** [Start Date]

## Stipend
- **Amount:** INR 10,000 per month, payable in accordance with company payroll schedule and subject to applicable taxes and deductions.

## Work Location and Schedule
- **Location:** Completely remote (based in Bengaluru).  
- Working hours and schedule will be agreed with your Reporting Manager. Reasonable flexibility may be required to collaborate with the team.

## Reporting
- **Reporting Manager:** [Reporting Manager]

## Conditions of Offer
- This offer is conditional upon satisfactory background verification and your acceptance of Omninuera’s company policies (including but not limited to confidentiality, IT acceptable use, code of conduct, and any other applicable policies).  
- You must complete any onboarding paperwork and checks required by the company prior to your start date.

## Confidentiality
During the internship and thereafter, you shall keep confidential all proprietary and confidential information of Omninuera and shall not disclose or use such information except as needed to perform your duties. This obligation survives the termination of your internship.

## Intellectual Property (IP) Assignment
You agree that any inventions, designs, developments, discoveries, works of authorship, trade secrets, or other intellectual property created, conceived, reduced to practice, or developed by you during the internship and related to Omninuera’s business or using company resources shall be the exclusive property of Omninuera. You shall promptly disclose such IP to Omninuera and execute any documents reasonably requested to assign rights to Omninuera.

## Compliance with Company Policies
You agree to comply with all Omninuera policies and procedures, as may be updated from time to time, including those relating to confidentiality, data protection, acceptable use, workplace conduct, and health and safety.

## Notice and Termination
- Either party may terminate this internship with **one (1) week’s** written notice.  
- Omninuera may terminate the internship **immediately for cause**, which includes but is not limited to breach of confidentiality, gross misconduct, material non-compliance with company policies, or actions that harm the company’s business or reputation.

## Data Protection and Privacy
Omninuera will process personal data provided by you in accordance with applicable data protection laws and company policies. By accepting this offer, you consent to such processing for purposes related to your internship, background checks, payroll, and HR administration.

## Taxes and Benefits
This is a stipend-based internship. You will not be eligible for regular employee benefits unless explicitly stated in writing. You are responsible for any personal tax liabilities arising from the stipend, pursuant to applicable law.

## Acceptance
To accept this offer, please sign and date below and return a scanned copy by the date indicated by your contact at Omninuera.

---

## Legal review recommended
Please have Legal review the following sections for compliance and appropriate scope:
- Confidentiality clause (scope and duration).  
- Intellectual Property / IP Assignment (scope, assignment mechanics, moral rights, and remuneration language if required).  
- Notice and Termination (definition of "cause" and termination rights).  
- Background verification conditions and any withdrawal rights.  
- Data protection and privacy wording (consent language and cross-border data transfers if applicable).  
- Any restrictive clauses or post-internship obligations.

